title: Ryan Long: Canadian Garbage
description:
Kippy and Foley are back to put comedian Ryan Long to the garbage test. Ryan talks growing up in Canada, trying to be a rockstar and shares some hilariously trashy stories. You know Ryan Long from his wildly successful YouTube videos and host of the Boyscast.
